      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CYNICAL (3) is a progressive gelding who made it five wins of the trot when coming from a much wider barrier to cruise home by 10m first up here last week. Should be improved by that and draws well so can continue his march through the grades. WICKED CONFESSION (1) has tackled the top mares at her last couple and did a great job to place after racing wide in the Queen Elizabeth II Mile last start. Draws out and tackles the boys but she is a talented mare on the up. LAYDEN (8) was held up when tackling stronger company last week. Draws wider but the prior form was good and he is better off in this company. TUKAHA (6) chased some handy rivals when fourth in the Regional Championship State Final last start and came from this barrier when winning at this circuit and distance prior. ISLA ROCHELLE (4) draws deeper but was good when placed in a handy line-up of mares last week.",
